            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 16 • Politely Disagreeing With Someone</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "If Kroll Enterprises doesn't take action soon, the company is going to be in financial trouble. Joel and Kathy have different opinions on how to cut costs at the company."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kathy:</b> We're going to be <b>in the red</b> again this year."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Joel:</b> I think we <b>should cut back on</b> employee health benefits. We could <b>save a bundle</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kathy:</b> True, it might help the <b>bottom line</b>, but our employees would be really unhappy. I would only recommend it as a <b>last resort</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Joel:</b> Well, we need to do some <b>belt-tightening</b>. We can either have a salary freeze or we can cut back on their health benefits. I think I've chosen <b>the lesser of two evils</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kathy:</b> Another salary freeze is <b>out of the question</b>. All our best employees will quit."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Joel:</b> I'm caught <b>between a rock and a hard place</b>. I have to cut costs."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kathy:</b> Do you really? I don't think cutting costs is <b>the name of the game</b>. I think the secret is figuring out how to increase our sales."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Joel:</b> How do you suggest we <b>pull that off</b>?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kathy:</b> Let's meet with the other vice presidents and <b>bat around some ideas</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Joel:</b> We can talk <b>until we're blue in the face</b>. We need to take action now."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kathy:</b> It's clear that you and I don't see eye-to-eye. For now, <b>let's just agree to disagree</b>."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
